data.description: Welcome to 48 Lott Avenue, a well-maintained four-unit (C3), free-market rental building available for the first time in 40 years. This semi-detached property features (2) 2-bedroom, 1 bathroom, and (2) 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartments with a fully finished basement. Each apartment is newly renovated and has been kept in excellent condition. The roof and mechanicals are all updated, there is a brand new water heater and a gas boiler. Access to transportation includes the 3 train at Saratoga Avenue station and multiple bus lines. Here's a terrific opportunity to grow your wealth and build your multi-family real estate portfolio in NYC. Two of the units are occupied and can be delivered vacant.
